route.name: Camp Sherman Splendor: Family Overnighter
route.description: Family bikepacking overnighter in an incredibly gorgeous place. Lots of camping options from multiple established campgrounds to dispersed camping. Variety of surfaces ranging from singletrack to red dirt to paved. Opportunities along the way to grab a bite at the Camp Sherman store, visit the fish hatchery, fly fish, or hike along the Metolius.
